data.description: Charming 1 story home w/open floor plan & lots of upgrades. Beautifully maintained home-move in ready. Located on a nice size lot. It has a covered patio, multiple decks, built-in bench seating, a privacy wall, and hot tub. Large combination breakfast room with remodeled kitchen that features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, granite island or breakfast table, wine cooler, & granite breakfast bar with pendant lights. Don't miss all the upgraded light fixtures, plumbing fixtures and ceiling fans. Spacious master bedroom has recessed ceiling, ceiling fan, huge walk-in closet. The remodeled master bath has granite double vanity, separate make up area  & separate glass enclosed shower. The converted garage is the 4th bedroom, which could also be a media room or game room with large walk-in closets. The family room features a very appealing built-in TV and electric fireplace making it the perfect place to entertain. This home has it all. You must see to appreciate all the loving care in this Bulverde Village home.
